title: Closer To The Truth [Target Deluxe Edition] - Cher - 320 Kbps -
description:
Closer to the Truth is the twenty-sixth studio album by American singer-actress Cher, released on September 20, 2013 by Warner Bros. Records. Work on the record began in 2011 after her appearance in the movie Burlesque and on its soundtrack and continued into the following two years. It is her first studio album since Living Proof (2001).
